{"tid":813023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(畫畫)原創畫風宣傳","createTime":"2018-09-10T06:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T03:08:05.000Z","uid":208103,"like":86,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9b0f73f0708ee8d6c02905f53453b977bbb3c6","tid":813023,"uid":208103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"先上圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/132311_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F132311_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=985d663e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/132313_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F132313_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9303413d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/132314_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F132314_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66f6b899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/132316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F132316_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6da89f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/132318_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F132318_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5d326a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先多謝各位巴/絲打睇完我啲奇奇怪怪嘅畫，希望你地可以睇埋以下我小小嘅自我介紹<br />\n<br />\n小弟今年19，公屋，啱啱dse grad，自細唔中意讀書，日日掛住玩嘅我喺中三冇揀科既權利，當然依家亦同ugc無緣，最後好似為讀而讀咁揀咗一個hd<br />\n<br />\n番咗一個星期已經想quit<br />\n<br />\n然而呢個世界讀唔成書好似會死咁<br />\n<br />\n本身已經冇乜朋友，大家開學又少咗聯絡，同屋企人又冇幾句，自己一個真係好抑鬱，訓醒繼續訓，逃避現實，一邊打機一邊不安，係至今最難受嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n冇諗過死係因為畫畫<br />\n<br />\n我發現畫畫係我僅存嘅價值，技能，唯一會堅持落去既事<br />\n<br />\n因為唔中意讀書抑鬱到咁<br />\n但又因為日日上堂畫notes培養咗畫畫既興趣<br />\n<br />\n真係好諷刺<br />\n<br />\n最後決定番住工先，同時試吓畫畫呢條路<br />\n<br />\n今日呢個post，與其話係宣傳，不如話只係想同人講吓野，自己一個真係好抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n大家咩都可以問，咩都可以講<br />\n<br />\n如果你中意我啲畫...就真係我最大嘅榮幸<br />\n<br />\nIG:senyak2s<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.deviantart.com/senyak2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deviantart.com%2Fsenyak2s&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=70b676cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.deviantart.com/senyak2s</a><br />\n上面呢個有大圖<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位"},{"pid":"3c88e8ae6f84afb98eff48720271f6d48ded903c","tid":813023,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"同你一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aeed3792262f869eb28fa518ca7258496e8b1a","tid":813023,"uid":208103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c88e8ae6f84afb98eff48720271f6d48ded903c","tid":813023,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"同你一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"quit hd?"},{"pid":"bdecfb9d1091a91c5366d22a00033477b0b38155","tid":813023,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23aeed3792262f869eb28fa518ca7258496e8b1a","tid":813023,"uid":208103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c88e8ae6f84afb98eff48720271f6d48ded903c","tid":813023,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"同你一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"quit hd?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:39:10.000Z","msg":