540a","tid":813023,"uid":14715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:40:50.000Z","msg":"樓主可以試下幅畫有個主題， 好似動物風景咁.."},{"pid":"f58a1909ea7071e57073f52156e46282ae7c8c64","tid":813023,"uid":208103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"重po<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/142749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F142749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9d34b6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一把刀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/142804_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F142804_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fc9496bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6a890ddfb88faabb49e56d5cd46513d8a5a3d75","tid":813023,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得 design嘅sense，art嘅techniques都可以練返嚟<br />\n<br />\nart都有design嘅過程<br />\ndesign又有art<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過fine art就真係唔係design嘅範籌喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝術理論要學可能要用好多時間<br />\n<br />\n但係佢哋對構圖好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n同埋學呢啲對自己嘅觀察力好有益<br />\n尤其好多畫其實compose得唔好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人識畫畫   畫到上天下海<br />\n但係設計美學，美感唔係個個都學過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我可以講嘅係，簡潔嘅構圖永遠無死"},{"pid":"3552ab939e5b0c4a92288b860792ca4139645d87","tid":813023,"uid":208103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/171437_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F171437_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f467fceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n象頭<br />\n<br />\n聽完大家嘅建議，嘗試用自己風格畫動物"}]}